{"tid":1597252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係英國擺咗一個小型連儂牆 冇歐洲人或者英國人對\"Anti-Chinazi\"反感","createTime":"2019-09-27T01:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T11:59:53.000Z","uid":259858,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5f777250a7c8e1656a3841f4146bba090eee33","tid":1597252,"uid":259858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:08:15.000Z","msg":"話說今日 U 有個fairs<br />\n我就同班friend搞咗個連儂牆 同埋周圍派傳單<br />\n咁我哋諗住試試水溫 喺個連儂牆其中一張poster 印有Anti-Chinazi嘅字眼<br />\n本身唔係特登嘅 只係印咗唔想嘥就貼埋上去<br />\n點知就比我發現啲英國人 對於Anti-chinazi呢個字眼根本一啲都唔反感反而仲好贊同 佢哋仲話&quot;We are fully support with the Hong Kong Protester&quot;.<br />\n反而一班中國嘅學生圍觀並且感到極度不滿 但我睇到佢哋面上嘅皺眉都感到十分興奮<br />\n<br />\n基於早前攬炒巴話呢個字眼過於敏感 所以改咗另外一個字眼<br />\n我每次串親都係Total唔識串((我英文差<br />\n<br />\n但係我想問其實你哋有冇真正係歐洲街頭 試過水溫?<br />\n個人認為Anti-Chinazi比另一字眼更為可以達到效果<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">純粹好奇一問 不分化不割蓆</span></span>"},{"pid":"91df5a55df1d1483fae4839f4ab46151c9ff882b","tid":1597252,"uid":259858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/djOJgTj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdjOJgTj.jpg&h=dfddd278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ho1uWTk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fho1uWTk.png&h=472a97ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsGyD6H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqsGyD6H.png&h=a9eb0b6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVaWBTo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVaWBTo.jpg&h=cc551c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FjNNJyp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjNNJyp.jpg&h=fccd9197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vX9WTq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u